net.sourceforge.jiu.apps
Interface MenuIndexConstants

All Known Implementing Classes:
EditorState, OperationProcessor
public interface MenuIndexConstants

Constant int values for all menu items. Some of these menu items denote operations which can be performed by OperationProcessor.

Author:
Marco Schmidt
